,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"商店街のおじさん","body":"そうか、それは残念だな。\nこの前も店の前を掃除してたらわざわざ話しかけに来てくれてね。\nあの子を見てると、こっちまで元気になるよ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"ふふ、それ香澄に言っておきますね。\nたぶんすっごい喜ぶと思います","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"event61-01-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"りみ","body":"あ、あの……っ。\nお祭りの時は、いろいろ私達の味方をしてくれて\nありがとうございましたっ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"awate01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"event61-01-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"商店街のおじさん","body":"ははは、お礼を言うのはこっちだよ。\nあのお祭り以降、地域の人達もこの商店街のことを\nちゃんと考えてくれるようになってね","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"商店街のおじさん","body":"あの時、君達が一生懸命動いてくれたことで、\n私達もしっかりしなきゃって思えたよ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinis